<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Iniciar Sesión - PelisPlus</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #06060c; color: #f1f1f1; }
        .page { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem; }
        .panel { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; background: rgba(11,13,22,.96); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); border-radius: 22px; box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.35); padding: 2.5rem; }
        h1 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 2rem; color: #e50914; }
        p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        label { display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; font-size: .95rem; color: #ccc; }
        input { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); background: #11131f; color: #fff; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-size: 1rem; }
        .btn { width: 100%; border: none; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e50914, #ff6b6b); color: #fff; padding: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: transform .2s ease; }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .small { color: #7d7d8c; text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .small a { color: #e50914; text-decoration: none; }
        .small a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .link-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: .9rem; }
        .link-row a { color: #ccc; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="panel">
            <h1>Iniciar Sesión</h1>
            <p>Accede a tu cuenta y sigue disfrutando de las mejores películas y promociones.</p>
            <form action="/loginCliente" method="POST">
                <label for="email">Correo electrónico</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="tucorreo@ejemplo.com" required>
                <label for="password">Contraseña</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="●●●●●●●●" required>
                <div class="link-row">
                    <a href="/register">Crear cuenta</a>
                    <a href="#">¿Olvidaste tu contraseña?</a>
                </div>
                <button class="btn" type="submit">Entrar</button>
            </form>
            <p class="small">¿No tienes cuenta? <a href="/register">Regístrate aquí</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>